&lt;h1 id="use-good-notation"&gt;Use good notation&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By relieving the brain of all unnecessary work, a good notation sets it free to concentrate on more advanced problems, and, in effect, increases the mental power of the race.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;— Alfred North Whitehead, &amp;ldquo;An Introduction to Mathematics&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good notation can make the difference between a readable paper and an unreadable one.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Write professionally</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/en/write-professionally/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 May 2007 20:15:35 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/en/write-professionally/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/zh/write-professionally.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;
